snippet.title: Rebots - Game Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Rebots is a first-person resource management game about running jobs for picky aliens! It’s your task to journey to diverse asteroids, terraform the land, gather resources through bot automation, and fulfill clients' needs!

Wishlist Rebots now! 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/993030/Rebots/
